Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,11比6
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,月本勝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,小泉老頭 萬事休矣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不過他身體還真是不錯
